# Docs workspace.
# docs/ holds COMMITTED text docs (guides, ADRs, runbooks, and
# DUAL-ACCESSIBILITY.md — which the CI check-testids guard depends on).
# Tracked .md/.mdx/.html stay in git. The following are kept on disk but NOT
# tracked: the archive folder, binary .docx planning docs, and the local-only
# droplet setup guide. (Previously a blanket `/docs/` ignore here was
# contradicted by 63 already-tracked files; replaced with targeted rules.)
docs/archive/
docs/linkedin/
docs/*.docx
docs/parametric-memory-whitepaper.pdf
docs/WEB-DROPLET-SETUP-GUIDE.md

